      %h2 Supporting quick and effective product evaluation
      %span Intercom Growth team - Spring 2017

    %h6 The team and my role
    %p Our team included a PM, a User Research, two engineers and myself as the product designer. I would  own the design of the solution from concept to final interaction and visual design and collaborte with PM, Research, Engineerring and external stakeholders thorughout the project.

