    %h6 The problem
    %p Challenges and blockers exist for people who try to evaluate our product. The more difficult it is to evaluate, the less likely people are to switch.

    %h6 Our hypothesis
    %p If we could make our product quicker to effectively evaluate than competitor products, we would have a competitive advantage.

    %h6 The challenge
    %p How might we enable people to quickly know if Intercom Respond meets their Help Desk requirements?

    %p Using a design sprint format, we assessed competitive products and explored possible solutions as a team

