    %h6 Choose your own adventure
    %p Proposal: Provide multiple paths for evaluating to accommodate different evaluation preferences.

    %p We had learned that some people are really motivated to evaluate by diving into the product and exploring on their own. Others prefer to be guided and shown how things work.

